<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>GitHub Actions Automation on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/apm/15-appd-workshop/6-smartagent/3-github-actions/</link><description>Recent content in GitHub Actions Automation on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/apm/15-appd-workshop/6-smartagent/3-github-actions/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Architecture &amp; Design</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/apm/15-appd-workshop/6-smartagent/3-github-actions/1-architecture/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/apm/15-appd-workshop/6-smartagent/3-github-actions/1-architecture/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="system-architecture"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;System Architecture&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#system-architecture" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The GitHub Actions-based Smart Agent deployment system uses a self-hosted runner within your AWS VPC to orchestrate deployments to multiple target hosts via SSH.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="high-level-architecture"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;High-Level Architecture&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#high-level-architecture" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;mermaid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;graph TB
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; subgraph Internet
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; GH[GitHub.com&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Repository &amp;amp; Actions]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; User[Developer&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Local Machine]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; end
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
