&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; subgraph SG[&amp;#34;Security Group: smartagent-lab&amp;#34;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; Runner[Self-hosted Runner&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;EC2 Instance&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;172.31.1.x]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; 
